\id 2CO 2 Corinthians in Boko, Ross Jones 2/08
\h 2 Kↄlɛnideↄ
\toc1 Kↄlɛnideↄ lá plaade
\toc2 2 Kↄlɛnideↄ
\toc3 2Kln
\mt1 KƆLƐNIDEƆ LÁ PLAADE
\imt1 Yã́ pↄ́ kú láɛ bee guuↄ
\ip Kↄlɛnideↄ lá plaadeɛ bee lɛ́ Kↄlɛni Yesudeↄ ↄkaakↄ̃'ↄu ń Pↄluo yã'owɛ̃ɛ. An gbɛ̃eↄ tàaekɛ̀ɛ̀ yãa, aa seakɛ̀ aà gↄ̃a Lua zĩna ũwa. Pↄlu ye wàↄ na ń kↄ̃o, ↄ̃ à azĩa yã́ bↄↄlɛkɛ̀nɛ́ ń yeańzio. A ònɛ́ lá a pↄ kɛ̀ na gↄↄ pↄ́ a ń baona mà (7.5-15).
\ip À kai pↄ́ à a le Ɛfɛsɛ bùsuu bↄↄlɛkɛ̀nɛ́ (1.1-11), ↄ̃ à taasi pↄ́ á kɛ̀ Kↄlɛniↄ yã́ dↄ̀ńgu. Yã́piↄ píiá aà Kilisi zĩnakɛyãↄnɛ. À yã́ pↄ́ tò a yã'ònɛ́ pãsĩpãsĩ a lá sɛ̃́ia guu bↄↄlɛkɛ̀nɛ́ ń lá a pↄnakɛ̀ gbɛzã, kɛ́ a yã́pi oa gbɛsù (1.12-7.16).
\ip Yude Yesudeↄ kámasakaa yã́ musu (8-9), à wabikɛ̀ Kↄlɛnideↄwa aa gbada ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndoo, asa à mɛ̀: Á wa Dii Yesu Kilisi gbɛ̃kɛ dↄ̃. Aà pↄde'ia à gↄ̃̀ pↄsaide ũ á yã́i, ↄ̃ aà pↄsaidekɛ guu à á kɛ́ pↄdeↄ ũ. (8.9)
\ip Lápi láakĩi (10-13) Pↄlu a yã'oa lìlɛ. À ɛ̀a sù gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aalɛ a dilɛ zĩna ũoↄ yã́wa. Ɔ̃ lápì yã́ mìdɛ ń gbɛ̃kɛkɛakↄ̃ɛo (13.11-13).
\ip Wásu to Pↄlu azĩa yã'oa ń nↄ̀sɛpuao wá sã́são. I kɛ aàzĩa bↄa maa ge aàzĩa yã́zɛ'ea àlɛ yáo, àlɛ a zĩnakɛ'iko ↄlↄnɛ́ɛ, kɛ́ wà e Yesu Kilisi baona sí, wí aà dↄ̃ Dii ũ.
\c 1
\s1 Nↄ̀sɛninia
\p 
\v 1 Mámɛmaa Kilisi Yesu zĩna Pↄlu lá Lua yeiwa ń wá gbɛ̃do Timↄteeo, wámɛ wa láɛ bee kɛ̃̀ Lua gãlide pↄ́ kú Kↄlɛniↄnɛ ń Lua gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kú Gɛlɛsi bùsuuↄ píi.
\v 2 Lua wá Mae ń Dii Yesu Kilisio gbɛ̃kɛkɛɛ́, i á gba aafia.
\p 
\v 3 Wà Lua wá Dii Yesu Kilisi Mae sáaukpa, Mae Lua sósobide gbɛ̃nↄsɛnininapi.
\v 4 Ì wá nↄ̀sɛ níniwɛ̃ɛ wá ĩadama píi guu, kɛ́ wà e gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kú baa ĩadama kpeletaa guuↄ nↄ̀sɛ níninɛ́ sↄ̃ ń nↄ̀sɛ nínibↄ pↄ́ Lua wá nↄ̀sɛ nìniowɛ̃ɛo.
\v 5 Lá taasi pↄ́ Kilisi kɛ̀ ì liwázi, màa lↄ wá nↄ̀sɛ ì níni maamaa Kilisi yã́i.
\v 6 Tó wà wá wɛtã̀, á nↄ̀sɛninia ń á bↄao yã́iɛ. Tó Lua wá nↄ̀sɛ nìni, á nↄ̀sɛninia yã́iɛ, kɛ́ à e taasi doũ pↄ́ wálɛ kɛ fↄ̃́.
\v 7 Wá á náai vĩ seasai, asa wá dↄ̃ lá á bàa kú ń taasi pↄ́ Kilisi kɛ̀o, á bàa kú ń nↄ̀sɛniniapio lↄ.
\p 
\v 8 Gbɛ̃́ↄ, wá ye àↄ dↄ̃ lá wà wá wɛtã̀ Azi bùsuu. À tↄ̃̀wá maamaa, a dɛ wá gbãa lɛ́a, baa wá wɛ̃ni wá wɛ́ dↄi lↄ seo.
\v 9 Yã́ daawála, wálɛ e wa gaɛ. Bee wá lé kɛ́ wásu zɛ ń wázĩa gbãaoo, sema Lua pↄ́ ì gɛↄ vu gbãa.
\v 10 À wá bↄ́ kai zↄ̃ↄ guu, mɛ́ a wá bↄu. Aàpi wá wɛ́ dↄi aà wá bↄu lↄ
\v 11 wabi pↄ́ álɛ kɛwɛ̃ɛ sabai. Beewa gbɛ̃́ↄ Lua sáaukpa dasi wá yã́ musu gbɛ̃kɛ pↄ́ a kɛ̀wɛ̃ɛ gbɛ̃́ dasiↄ wabikɛawɛ̃ɛ yã́i.
\s1 Pↄlu wɛ̃́lɛgɛ gbooa
\p 
\v 12 Yã́ pↄ́ wi a ĩ́anadãn kɛ: Wá làasoo daa doũ, asa ń Lua gbãao wá kú ń nↄ̀sɛpuao mↄafilisai dṹnia guu, atɛ̃sa á kĩ́i. Dṹnia ↄ̃nↄ wá kuòo, sema Lua gbɛ̃kɛ.
\v 13 Wili láe kɛ̃́ɛ́o, sema pↄ́ i a kyokɛ á dↄ̃ bàasio.
\v 14 Lá á wá dↄ̃ gĩa yↄↄ, má ye à wá dↄ̃ sã́asã, kɛ́ à ĩ́anadã wá yã́ musu Dii Yesu mↄ́zĩ, lá wá dã á yã́ musuwa.
\p 
\v 15-16 Kↄ̃ náaikɛapi guu má dìlɛ yãa ma Masedoni gɛa guu mà bↄlɛ á gwai káau, mí ɛa su ń á kĩ́io, í báaa e gɛ̃n pla, í dↄnlɛkɛmɛɛ ma Yude gɛa guu.\f + \fr 1.15-16 \ft Zĩn 19.21\f*
\v 17 Kɛ́ ma gɛa bee dìlɛ, ma lɛplayã'ò yã̀? Tó má dìlɛ mà yãkɛ, dṹnia yã́ ì dↄaamɛɛ, ↄ̃ ì kɛmɛɛ kã́ndo ao ao ge aawo aawo ũa?
\v 18 Lá Lua náai vĩ, yã́ pↄ́ wá òɛ́ dɛ ao aawo ũo.
\v 19 Lua Nɛ́ Yesu Kilisi pↄ́ mapi ń Silivɛ̃ɛo ń Timↄteeo\f + \fr 1.19 \ft Zĩn 18.5\f* wa aà yã́ waasokɛ̀ɛ́ á gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ì mɛ ao aawo no, Lua pↄ́ ì mɛ aon aà ũ.
\v 20 Asa lɛ́ pↄ́ Lua gbɛ̃̀ píi sĩana ì kɛ aà guuɛ. Ayãmɛto ń Yesu Kilisipi tↄ́o ↄ̃ wì mɛ ãmi, Lua tↄbↄa yã́i.
\v 21 Lua mɛ́ wá zĩ́napɛ̀lɛ naa Kilisiwa ń ápiↄ, à wá dílɛ adoa,
\v 22 à a seela kɛ̀wá, à a Nisĩna dà wá sↄ̃u gba pↄ́ Lua dↄ̀aa dàwɛ̃ɛ ũ.
\p 
\v 23 Lua mɛ́ ma seelade ũ, a ma nↄ̀sɛ dↄ̃. Kɛ́ má ye ĩadawáo yã́i mi gɛ́ Kↄlɛni lↄo.
\v 24 I kɛ wálɛ gbãamↄɛ́ á luanaaikɛa guu no, asa a zɛ̀dↄu kↄ̀, wálɛ zĩkɛánↄ á pↄna yã́iɛ.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Ɔ̃ má è mazĩawa a maa mà mↄ́ á kĩ́i ń pↄyao lↄo.
\v 2 Tó ma á pↄ yàɛ́, démɛ a ma pↄ kɛ nai, mɛ́ i kɛ á gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ma á pↄ yàɛ́ↄ bàasio?
\v 3 Ma lakɛ̃̀ɛ́ màa, kɛ́ tó ma mↄ á gwai, á gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ á dɛ à ma pↄ kɛ naↄ su ma pↄ yaoɛ. Má á náai vĩ ápii, kɛ́ ma pↄna dɛ á pↄna ũ.
\v 4 Ma lápi kɛ̃̀ɛ́ ń pↄsiao ń nↄ̀sɛpusuo ń wɛ́'ioɛ, i kɛ kɛ́ mà á pↄ ya yã́i no, kɛ́ àↄ dↄ̃ lá ma yeaázi kà yã́iɛ.
\p 
\v 5 Lá gbɛ̃e pↄyayã kɛ̀, i kɛ ma pↄ a yào, ápiiɛ, ge á gbɛ̃eↄ, kɛ́ ma yã'oa su gɛ̃agɛ̃o.
\v 6 Ĩa pↄ́ á daside dà gbɛ̃́piwa mↄ̀wà.
\v 7 Ayãmɛto à sùuukɛaànↄ sa, à aà nↄ̀sɛ níniɛ̀, kɛ́ aà pↄsia zↄ̃ↄ su aà mↄ ĩ́io yã́i.
\v 8 Bee yã́i ma awakpàɛ́, à ↄlↄɛ̀ wásawasa kɛ́ á yeaàzi.
\v 9 A yã́i ma lápi kɛ̃̀ɛ́, ma likpàlɛwá mà e dↄ̃ tó á yã́ pↄ́ má òɛ́ kũa píi.
\v 10 Tó a sùuukɛ̀ ń gbɛ̃́o, mi kɛaànↄ sↄ̃ɛ. Sùuu pↄ́ má kɛ̀, tó yãe su ku, má kɛ̀ á yã́i Kilisi gɛ̃ɛ ũɛ,
\v 11 kɛ́ Setãu su ↄ̃nↄkɛwɛ̃ɛo yã́i, asa wá gí aà kↄ̃ni dↄ̃io.
\s1 Luabaakuańnↄ yã́ dafu
\p 
\v 12 Kɛ́ ma gɛ Kilisi baokpai Toloasi, Dii zɛpòomɛɛ,
\v 13 ãma ma nisĩna zɛao, kɛ́ mi a gbɛ̃do Titu eo yã́i. Ɔ̃ ma lɛzàmá we, ma da Masedoni zɛ́u.\f + \fr 2.13 \ft Zĩn 20.1\f*
\p 
\v 14 Ma sáaukɛ̀ ń Luao, asa ìↄ dↄaawɛ̃ɛ gↄↄpiiɛ, wiↄ zĩ̀blenaↄ ũ naa Kilisiwa, wi aà dↄ̃a gĩ fã́ɛ gupiiu.
\v 15 Asa wá dɛ tulaleti gĩ na pↄ́ Kilisi kpàsa Luaɛ ũ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ àlɛ ń suabaↄ ń gbɛ̃́ vũaaaↄ guuɛ.
\v 16 Wá gɛ̀ gĩ ũ gbɛ̃eↄnɛ, ↄ̃ ì ga inɛ́. Wá wɛ̃ni gĩ ũ gbɛ̃́ kĩniↄnɛ, ↄ̃ ì wɛ̃ni inɛ́. Wá démɛ kà bee kɛai?
\v 17 Wá dɛ lán gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aaìↄ Lua yã́ laataↄwao. Naa Kilisiwa wi yã'o ń nↄ̀sɛpuao ń Lua dↄ̃ao a zĩnaↄ ũ.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Wa ɛa su wázĩa sáaukpaawa yã̀? Wá bàa kú ń seela lá pↄ́ wa kɛ̃̀ɛ́ ge pↄ́ á kɛ̃̀nɛ́o lán gbɛ̃eↄwa yã̀?
\v 2 Ámɛ á wá taalapi ũ, a kɛ̃a wá sↄ̃wa. Gbɛ̃́pii a fↄ̃ dↄ̃, i a kyokɛ.
\v 3 Á yã́ bↄ̀ gupuau, á dɛ lá pↄ́ Kilisi kɛ̃̀ a nà wá ↄzĩ ũ. I lápi kɛ̃́ ń gàalula ío no, a kɛ̃̀ ń Lua bɛ̃́ɛ Nisĩnaoɛ. I kɛ̃ gbɛ̀ pɛ̀pɛɛwa no,\f + \fr 3.3 \ft Bↄa 24.12\f* a kɛ̃̀ á sↄ̃waɛ.\f + \fr 3.3 \ft Zel 31.33, Eze 11.19\f*
\p 
\v 4 Wá a náai vĩ màa Lua aɛ ń Kilisi gbãao.
\v 5 I kɛ ń wázĩao wi ka wà mɛ zĩpi bↄ̀ wá gã̀uɛo, Lua mɛ́ wá káwà.
\v 6 Ɔ̃mɛ wá káwà, ↄ̃ wá dɛ aà bàa kua ń gbɛ̃́ↄ yã́ dafu zĩkɛnaↄ ũ.\f + \fr 3.6 \ft Zel 31.31\f* I kɛ ikoyã no, Lua Nisĩna yã́ɛ. Asa ikoyã ì ga inɛ́ɛ, Nisĩnapi sↄ̃ ì wɛ̃ni inɛ́.
\p 
\v 7 Kɛ́ Lua ikoyã kɛ̃̀ gbɛ̀ pɛ̀pɛɛwa, a gawi bↄ̀ Mↄizi oawa.\f + \fr 3.7 \ft Bↄa 34.29\f* Ń a tɛkɛa gɛ̃azɛakɛo Isailiↄ i fↄ̃ gwào. Tó zɛ́ pↄ́ ì ga inɛ́pi bↄ̀ ń gawi bee taao,
\v 8 Nisĩnapi zɛ́ gawi dɛai?
\v 9 Lá zɛ́ pↄ́ ì yãdańla gawi vĩ, zɛ́ pↄ́ ì to yã́ bↄńnↄ na gawi dɛa zↄ̃ↄ.
\v 10 Pↄ́ pↄ́ gawi vĩ yãa gawi vĩ lↄo, gawi pↄ́ dɛaàlapi yã́i.
\v 11 Tó pↄ́ gↄↄsoplana bↄ̀ ń gawio, pↄ́ pↄ́ ìↄ ku gawi dɛa zↄ̃ↄ.
\p 
\v 12 Wɛdↄa beei guu wi yã'o seasai.
\v 13 Wá dɛ lán Mↄiziwao. À sálana kù a oaa, kɛ́ Isailiↄ su a oa tɛkɛa pↄ́ lɛ́ gɛ̃zɛa láaa eo.\f + \fr 3.13 \ft Bↄa 34.33\f*
\v 14 An nↄ̀sɛ tàta, asa e gbã tó aalɛ Luabaakuańnↄ lá kyokɛ, sálana doũpi ìↄ kua ń làasooaɛ. Ìli goo, sema tó gbɛ̃́ naa Kilisiwa bàasio.
\v 15 E tia tó wàlɛ Mↄizi yã́ kyokɛ, sálanapi ìↄ kua ń làasooaɛ.
\v 16 Ãma tó aa zɛ̀ ń Diio, sálanapi a go ń làasooa.
\v 17 Diipi mɛ́ Lua Nisĩnapi ũ, mɛ́ gu pↄ́ Dii Nisĩnapi kuu, we wì gↄ̃ wɛ̃́ɛↄ ũ.
\v 18 Wá gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ pↄ́ gò wá oawaↄ, wálɛ Dii gawi ↄlↄnɛ́ lán díiwa, wiↄ li laaàwa, wá gawi iↄ kã́fĩ. Dii pↄ́ dɛ Lua Nisĩna ũpi zĩn we.
\c 4
\s1 Zĩnaↄ kua ga lɛ́zĩ
\p 
\v 1 Ayãmɛto lá Lua zĩ bee dàwɛ̃ɛ a sùuu guu, wá kúsu lí kwɛ́o.
\v 2 Wa ↄkpà asii wisaiyãↄzi, wili yãkɛ ń wɛzɛ̃oo, mɛ́ wili Lua yã́ koleo. Wi sĩana'ònɛ́ wásawasa wà wázĩa kɛkɛ gbɛ̃́piiɛ Lua dↄ̃a guuɛ.
\v 3 Tó baona pↄ́ wálɛ kpá ulɛaɛ, gbɛ̃́ vũaaaↄ ↄ̃ a ulɛanɛ́.
\v 4 Asa dṹniaɛ bee dii Yesusaideↄ wɛ́ vĩ̀akũ̀, kɛ́ aasu baona sí, Kilisi pↄ́ dɛ Lua taa ũ gawi gupunɛ́o yã́iɛ.
\v 5 Wá zĩa kpàwa wálɛ kɛo, Yesu Kilisi diikɛ kpàwa wálɛ kɛ, mɛ́ wálɛ zↄbleɛ́ aà yã́i.
\v 6 Lá Lua ò yãa, gu pu gusiau,\f + \fr 4.6 \ft Daa 1.3\f* à gupù wá sↄ̃u màa lↄ. Gupuapi dɛ aà gawi pↄ́ lɛ́ tɛkɛ Kilisi oawa dↄ̃a ũ.
\p 
\v 7 Ń beeo wá gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ wá àizɛɛ bee kũaↄ, wá dɛ lán gĩ̀ oowa, kɛ́ wà e dↄ̃ gbãa zↄ̃ↄ ì bↄ Lua kĩ́iɛ, wá kĩ́i no.
\v 8 Wìↄ ĩadawá gupiiuɛ, ń beeo wili fuo. Wi bílikɛ, ãma wá wɛ́ dↄa Luazi lí busao.
\v 9 Wì wá wɛtã, ãma Lua lí wá tó weo. Wì wá pã́lɛ, ãma wili gao.
\v 10 Gↄↄpii wá kú Yesu ga suawá guu, kɛ́ aà wɛ̃ni e bↄ gupuau wá mɛwa yã́i.
\v 11 Wá gbɛ̃́ bɛ̃́ɛↄ wiↄ ku ga lɛ́zĩ Yesu yã́i, kɛ́ aà wɛ̃ni e bↄ gupuau wá mɛ pↄ́ a ga guu yã́i.
\v 12 Màa gapi lɛ́ zĩkɛ wá guu, mɛ́ wɛ̃nipi lɛ́ zĩkɛ á guu.
\v 13 A kɛ̃a Lua taalau wà mɛ̀: Ma Lua náaikɛ̀ ↄ̃ ma yã'ò.\f + \fr 4.13 \ft Soũ 116.10\f* Wápiↄ sↄ̃ wa Lua náai doũpi kɛ̀, ↄ̃ wálɛ yã'o a yã́i.
\v 14 Asa wá dↄ̃ lá Lua Dii Yesu bↄ̀ gau, a wá bↄaànↄ gau sↄ̃, i wá kpá a kùɛ sãnu ń ápiↄ.
\v 15 Beeↄ lɛ́ wá le píi á yã́i, Lua gbɛ̃kɛ i li gbɛ̃́ dasidea, aà sáaukpaa i kã́fĩ aà tↄbↄa yã́i.
\s1 Wɛdↄa mɛ̀ dafui
\p 
\v 16 Ayãmɛto wá kúsu lí kwɛ́o. Baa tó wá mɛkaa lɛ́ yaikɛ, wá guu ìↄ dafukũ lá gu lɛ́ dↄɛ.
\v 17 Wá ĩadama gↄↄ do lɛɛnaɛ bee lɛ́ gawi zↄ̃ↄ láasai iwɛ̃ɛ, a dɛ beeao.
\v 18 Wá wɛ́ kú pↄ́ pↄ́ wì wɛsiɛ kĩ́io, sema pↄ́ pↄ́ wìli wɛsiɛo. Asa pↄ́ pↄ́ wì wɛsiɛá gↄↄpla pↄ́ɛ. Pↄ́ pↄ́ wìli wɛsiɛo sↄ̃ ìↄ ku gↄↄpiiɛ.
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 Wá dↄ̃ tó wá sↄ pↄ́ wá kúu kpɛ́ ũ dṹnia guuɛ bee yàa, Lua a kpɛ́ pↄ́ wi dↄ ń ↄoo kpáwá a bɛ e gↄↄpii.
\v 2 Wi we sↄpi guu fɛ̀ɛɛ, wá ye luabɛ pↄ́pi daɛ,
\v 3 asa tó wa bↄ sↄu, wáↄ ku mɛsaio.
\v 4 Gↄↄ pↄ́ wá kú sↄɛ bee guu, wi we fɛ̀ɛɛ lá wá asosɛawa. I kɛ wá ye bↄ a guu no, wá ye luabɛ pↄ́ daɛ, kɛ́ wɛ̃ni wá sↄ pↄ́ ì gapi mↄ́.
\v 5 Bee yã́i ↄ̃ Lua wá kɛ́i, ↄ̃ à a Nisĩna kpàwá gba pↄ́ à dↄ̀aa dàwɛ̃ɛ ũ.
\p 
\v 6 A yã́i tò wá sↄ̃ ìↄ dilɛa. Wá dↄ̃ gↄↄ pↄ́ wá mɛɛ bee ku, wá kú Dii kĩ́io.
\v 7 Asa Dii náai wá kuò, i kɛ wɛsia pↄelɛ yã́ no.
\v 8 Wá sↄ̃ ìↄ dilɛa. Bↄa sↄu gɛa Dii kĩ́i mɛ́ maawɛ̃ɛ.
\v 9 Kua mɛ guun nò, bↄa a guun nò, wiↄ wɛɛlɛ wá yã́ kaaàgu.
\v 10 Asa Kilisi aↄ zↄ̃lɛa a gĩ́naa, wápii wí bↄ zɛ aà aɛ, i fĩabo wá baadeɛ aà kua mɛ guu yãkɛawa, a maa ge a vãi.\f + \fr 5.10 \ft Lom 14.10-12\f*
\s1 Gbɛ̃nazĩnaↄ kɛa na ń Luao zĩ
\p 
\v 11 Lá wálɛ vĩakɛ Diiɛ màa, wi wɛɛlɛ gbɛ̃́ↄ yã́pi zɛ́ e. Lua wá sã́asã dↄ̃, mɛ́ wá ye à wá dↄ̃ á sↄ̃u màa.
\v 12 Wálɛ wázĩa sáaukpaɛ́ lↄ no, wálɛ á gba zɛ́ à ĩ́anadã wá yã́ musuɛ, í e yã́zãsi gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ì ĩ́anadã pↄ́ pↄ́ àlɛ e ń wɛ́o, i kɛ sↄ̃̀ yã́ nowa.
\v 13 Tó álɛ e wá liaaaɛ, Lua yã́iɛ. Tó wa su wá dↄ̀ↄwa, á yã́iɛ.
\v 14 Asa Kilisi yeawázi yã́ mɛ́ wá kũa gbãa. Wá è tó gbɛ̃́ mɛ̀ndo gà gbɛ̃́pii gɛ̃ɛ ũ, aa gà ḿpiin we.
\v 15 À gà gbɛ̃́pii gɛ̃ɛ ũ, kɛ́ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ gↄ̃̀ↄ su wàↄ kú ńzĩa pↄ́ ũ lↄo, sema gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ gà ń gɛ̃ɛ ũ à vù pↄ́.
\p 
\v 16 Bee yã́i wili gbɛ̃e gwa lá dṹnia ì aà gwawa tia lↄo. Baa kɛ́ wá Kilisi dↄ̃ lá dṹnia aà dↄ̃wa yãa, wá aà dↄ̃ màa tia lↄo.
\v 17 Tó gbɛ̃́ naa Kilisiwa, gbɛ̃́ dafuɛ. Aà kua zi gɛ̃̀, a dafu mɛ́ mↄ̀.
\v 18 Bee bↄ̀ Lua kĩ́i píiɛ. À wá kɛanↄ na ń Kilisi gbãao, ↄ̃ à gbɛ̃́ↄ kɛa naanↄ zĩ dàwɛ̃ɛ.
\v 19 Kilisi sabai Lua dṹnia kɛ̀anↄ na gbɛ̃́ↄ tàaeↄ yãdasai. À gbɛ̃́ↄ kɛaanↄ napi yãdàwɛ̃ɛ.
\v 20 Beewa Kilisi gɛ̃ɛↄn wá ũ. Lua lɛ́ gbɛ̃́ↄ sisi wá musu. Wa wabikɛ̀wá Kilisi gbɛu, à kɛ na ń Luao.
\v 21 Lua tò duunsaide gↄ̃̀ duuna awakpabↄ ũ wá yã́i, kɛ́ naawà guu Lua i to yã́ bↄwanↄ na.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 Lá wálɛ zĩkɛ Luaɛ, wa awakpàɛ́, ásu to gbɛ̃kɛ pↄ́ Lua kɛ̀ɛ́ kɛ pão.
\v 2 Asa Lua mɛ̀:
\q1 Ma n yãmà a gↄↄwa,
\q1 ma dↄnlɛ suabagↄↄ.\f + \fr 6.2 \ft Isa 49.8\f*
\m Gↄↄ kà sa, gbã mɛ́ suabagↄↄpi ũ.
\p 
\v 3 Wili yã́ pↄ́ a to gbɛ̃́ fu kɛo, kɛ́ wasu wá zĩ sãa eo yã́i.
\v 4 Wi wá luazĩkɛnkɛ ↄlↄ gbɛ̃́ↄnɛ yã́pii guu. Wi mɛnafↄ̃ maamaa ń ĩadaawáo ń taasio ń wɛ́tɛ̃ao.
\v 5 Wà wá gbɛ̃́, wà wá ká kpɛ́u, wà fɛ̀lɛwanↄ. Wa zĩ gbãa kɛ̀, wi e i'òo, nↄana wá dɛ́.
\v 6 Wá ↄ̀lↄnɛ́ ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndoo ń dↄ̃ao ń sùuuo ń maakɛao ń nↄ̀sɛpuao ń yenzi mↄafilisaio
\v 7 ń sĩana'oao ń Lua gbãao. Wá maakɛbↄↄ kũa wá ↄplaau ń zɛɛo.
\v 8 Wì wá kpɛla, wì wá kpɛbↄ. Wì wá tↄ́ vãi sí, wì wá tↄnasi. Sĩandeↄn wá ũ, ↄ̃ wì wá dilɛ mↄafilideↄ ũ.
\v 9 Tↄdeↄn wá ũ, ↄ̃ wì wá dilɛ gbɛ̃andoↄ ũ. Wá bɛ̃́ɛɛ fá, ↄ̃ wì wá dilɛ gɛↄ ũ. Wì wá dilɛ pↄgbɛ̃aↄ ũ, ãma wìli wá dɛo.
\v 10 Wá pↄ ìↄ naɛ, ↄ̃ wìↄ wá dilɛ pↄsiadeↄ ũ. Wi gbɛ̃́ↄ kɛ ↄdeↄ ũ dasi, ↄ̃ wìↄ wá dilɛ taasideↄ ũ. Wá pↄ́pii vĩ, ↄ̃ wìↄ wá dilɛ pↄesaideↄ ũ.
\p 
\v 11 Kↄlɛnideↄ, wa yã'òɛ́ wásawasa, wa wá nↄ̀sɛ wɛ̃̀ɛ́.
\v 12 Wi wá nↄ̀sɛ kṹkpaɛ́o, ámɛ a á pↄ́ kũ̀kpawɛ̃ɛ.
\v 13 Ma yã'òɛ́ lán ma nɛ́ↄwaɛ. Lá wa wá nↄ̀sɛ wɛ̃̀ɛ́, à á nↄ̀sɛ wɛ̃wɛ̃ɛ sↄ̃.
\s1 Kɛ̃a Yesusaideↄwa
\p 
\v 14 Ásu nakↄ̃wa ń Yesusaideↄo. Kpelewa maa ń vãio aa gbɛ̃́kpa ń kↄ̃oi? Baa kpele gupua ń gusiao vĩ ń kↄ̃oi?
\v 15 Kilisi yã́ a kↄ̃sɛ ń Setãu pↄ́o kpelewa ni? Bↄ́ Yesude ń Yesusaideo vĩ ń kↄ̃oi?
\v 16 Kpelewa Lua kpɛ́ lɛ́ a kɛ doũ ń tã́aↄi? Lua bɛ̃́ɛ kpɛ́n wá ũ, lá a òwa à mɛ̀:
\q1 Máↄ kúńnↄ, máↄ bɛbɛ ń guu,\f + \fr 6.16 \ft 1Kln 3.16, 6.19\f*
\q1 míↄ dɛ ń Lua ũ,
\q1 aaiↄ dɛ ma gbɛ̃́ↄ ũ.\f + \fr 6.16 \ft Eze 37.27\f*
\m 
\v 17 Ayãmɛto Dii mɛ̀:
\q1 À kɛ̃́má, àliↄ kú ádoa,
\q1 ásu ↄkã pↄ́ gbãlɛawao,\f + \fr 6.17 \ft Isa 52.11\f*
\q1 mí á sí,
\v 18 míↄ dɛ á Mae ũ,
\q1 íↄ dɛ ma nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ ń ma nɛnↄɛↄ ũ.\f + \fr 6.18 \ft 2Sam 7.14\f*
\q1 Dii Gbãapiide mɛ́ ò.
\c 7
\p 
\v 1 Ma gbɛ̃́ yenzideↄ, lá Lua lɛgbɛ̃̀wɛ̃ɛ màa, wà kɛ̃ yã́ pↄ́ ì mɛ ń nisĩnao gbãlɛwa míↄmiↄ, wí wɛɛlɛ wà wá kua adoa lɛpapa vĩakɛa Luaɛ guu.
\s1 Pↄlu pↄ kɛa Kↄlɛnideↄwa na
\p 
\v 2 À wá kṹ ↄplapla. Wi tàaekɛ gbɛ̃eɛo, wi gbɛ̃e ↄ̃̀ↄkpao, wi gbɛ̃e taiinkɛo.
\v 3 Mi bee o mà yãdaála no. Má ò kↄ̀, wa gan nò, wá kún nò, á yã́ dↄ wá sↄ̃waɛ.
\v 4 Má á náai vĩ zↄ̃ↄ, mi ĩ́anadã á yã́ musu maamaa. Wɛ́tɛ̃a mↄawɛ̃ɛ guu píi ma nↄ̀sɛninia kpɛ lↄo, ma pↄ kɛ̀na yã́iyãi.
\v 5 Baa kɛ́ wa ka Masedoni bùsuu,\f + \fr 7.5 \ft 2Kln 2.13\f* wá mɛ i e dↄ̀o. Wɛ́tɛ̃a píi wá lé, wà fɛ̀lɛwá ń sòleo, ↄ̃ wá kú sↄ̃̀deedee guu.
\v 6 Ɔ̃ Lua pↄ́ ì yɛ̃̀ɛɛsaideↄ nↄ̀sɛ níni wá nↄ̀sɛ nìniwɛ̃ɛ Titu mↄa guu.
\v 7 I kɛ aà mↄa ado no, kɛ́ a aà nↄ̀sɛ nìniɛ̀ yã́iɛ lↄ. A òwɛ̃ɛ álɛ ma bɛɛkɛ, á kú déndↄ̃mɛɛ guu, a zɛmanↄ sa, ↄ̃ ma pↄna kã̀fĩ.
\p 
\v 8 Baa kɛ́ lá pↄ́ má kɛ̃̀ɛ́ á pↄ yà, má làasoo pãle dao. Ma làasoo pãle dà yãa, kɛ́ má è lápi á pↄ yà gↄↄpla,
\v 9 ãma ma pↄ kɛ̀na sa. I kɛ kɛ́ ma á pↄ yàɛ́ yã́i no, kɛ́ á pↄsia tò a nↄ̀sɛlìlɛ yã́iɛ. Á pↄyaapi bↄ̀ Lua kĩ́iɛ. Bee yã́i ásoo wá kɛ̀ɛ́o.
\v 10 Pↄsia pↄ́ bↄ̀ Lua kĩ́i ì to gbɛ̃́ nↄ̀sɛlilɛ Luapi i aà suaba líↄ déndↄ̃mɛɛ vĩo. Dṹnia pↄsia mɛ́ ì ga inɛ́.
\v 11 À gwa lá pↄsia pↄ́ bↄ̀ Lua kĩ́ipi zĩkɛ̀ á guu. Á mɛ wã̀ sa, a gi ń ázĩao, á pↄ fɛ̀lɛ, vĩa á kṹ, a ma bɛɛkɛ̀, a wɛtã̀, a vãikɛna swãgàga. Apii guu a ázĩa ↄ̀lↄnɛ́ kɛ́ á tàae vĩ yã́pi guuo.
\p 
\v 12 Baa kɛ́ ma lápi kɛ̃̀ɛ́, i kɛ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ tàaekɛ̀ ge gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ à tàaekɛ̀ɛ̀ yã́i no, má kɛ̃̀ Lua dↄ̃a guu, kɛ́ á yeawázi e bↄ gupuauɛ.
\v 13 Wá nↄ̀sɛninia bee bàasi, wá pↄna kã̀fĩ maamaa Titu pↄna yã́ musu, kɛ́ ápii á tò aà nisĩna sù yã́i.
\v 14 Ma ĩ́anadã̀ɛ̀ yãa á yã́ musu, i to wí ma kũo. Lá wa sĩana'òɛ́ yã́pii guu, màa wá ĩ́andãa Tituɛ kɛ̀ sĩana ũ.
\v 15 Lá a aà dìlɛ gbia a aà kpɛlà, mɛ́ a aà yãmà ápii, tó à làasookɛ̀ yã́piwa, aà nↄ̀sɛ ì ɛa yáalↄwáɛ.
\v 16 Ma pↄ kɛ̀na, kɛ́ má á náai vĩ yã́pii guu yã́i.
\c 8
\s1 Kↄ̃ kámasakaa
\p 
\v 1 Gbɛ̃́ↄ, wá ye àↄ gbɛ̃kɛ pↄ́ Lua kɛ̀ Yesude pↄ́ aa ku Masedoni bùsuu wɛ̃́lɛ ń wɛ̃́lɛoↄnɛ dↄ̃.
\v 2 An yↄ̃a ń ĩadaama pãsĩo guu, an pↄ kɛ̀na maamaa, ↄ̃ baa ń ń taaside búubuukɛo aa gbadà sↄũsↄũ.
\v 3 Má òɛ́ aa gbadà ń gbãa lɛ́u, a dɛ ń gbãa lɛ́a se.
\v 4 Aa gbɛ̀awá ńzĩa awa ń awao, wà ń gba zɛ́ ń ↄ e àↄ ku Lua gbɛ̃́ↄ kámasa guu.\f + \fr 8.4 \ft Lom 15.26\f*
\v 5 Aa kɛ̀ dɛ lá wá wɛ́ dↄia, aa ńzĩa kpà Diiwa gĩa ń wápiↄ lↄ lá Lua yeiwa.
\v 6 Ɔ̃ wa wabikɛ̀ Tituwa aà gɛ́ kámasa yã́ pↄ́ a dàalɛ á guu lɛkpaaĩi.
\v 7 Lá á gbãa yã́pii guu, luanaaikɛa ń yã'oao ń dↄ̃ao ń yã́pii ãiao ń á yeawázio, àↄ gbãa kámasapi kaa guu lↄ.
\p 
\v 8 I kɛ ma yãdìlɛɛ́ no, kↄai pↄ́ gbɛ̃pãleↄ kɛ̀ ↄ̃ má òɛ́, kɛ́ mà e mà á yea gbɛ̃́ↄzi sĩana dↄ̃.
\v 9 Á wá Dii Yesu Kilisi gbɛ̃kɛ dↄ̃. Aà pↄde'ia à gↄ̃̀ pↄsaide ũ á yã́i, ↄ̃ aà pↄsaidekɛ guu à á kɛ́ pↄdeↄ ũ.
\v 10 Lá má è yã́pi musun we. Bee kↄ̃sì ń á gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ a zɛ ń yã́pio za muyãa, mɛ́ á kɛ̀ↄ.
\v 11 À yã́pi lɛkpaaĩ sa. Lá á sↄu mà ń a kɛao, à kɛ á gbãa lɛ́u.
\v 12 Tó gbɛ̃́ gbadà ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndoo a pↄvĩa lɛ́u, bee ì ká, i kɛ pↄ́ pↄ́ a vĩo no.
\v 13 I kɛ áↄ taasikɛ gbɛ̃́ kĩniↄ aaↄ namable no. Àↄ kpaaĩa.
\v 14 Tia kɛ́wa pↄ́ pↄ́ diázi à yoonɛ́ an pↄ́kɛ̃sãama guu. Gↄↄewa sↄ̃, pↄ́ pↄ́ dińzi aai ɛa yooɛ́ á pↄ́kɛ̃sãawá guu. Beewa áↄ kpaaĩa.
\v 15 Lá a kɛ̃a láuwa wà mɛ̀:
\q1 Sɛ̀lɛnzↄ̃ↄde pↄ́ i fɛ̃o,
\q1 yↄↄnde pↄ́ i kɛ̃́são.\f + \fr 8.15 \ft Bↄa 16.18\f*
\s1 Pↄlu Tituↄ sáaukpaa Kↄlɛnideↄnɛ
\p 
\v 16 Ma sáaukɛ̀ ń Luao, kɛ́ a tò á yã́ dↄ Titu sↄ̃wa lamawa.
\v 17 À wá yãmà, aà mɛ wã̀ à mↄ á gwai, àlɛ mↄ́ teasi no.
\v 18 Wá gbɛ̃do pↄ́ aà tↄ́ lìgua Yesudeↄ guu píi baonakpaa musu ↄ̃ wá dàɛ̀.
\v 19 Bee gbɛa lↄ Yesudeↄ aà sɛ̀ aà gɛ́wanↄ kámasa zĩ pↄ́ wálɛ kɛ kɛi. Wálɛ zĩpi kɛ Dii tↄbↄa yã́iɛ ń nↄ̀sɛmaa pↄ́ wá dào.
\v 20 Wálɛ gbɛ̃́ↄ wá tàae'ea gba zↄ̃ↄ pↄ́ na wá ↄzĩ yã́ musu abaa bↄ.
\v 21 I kɛ yã́ pↄ́ maa Diiɛ ↄ̃ wálɛ wɛɛlɛ adoo, ń pↄ́ pↄ́ maa gbɛ̃nazĩnaↄnɛo lↄɛ.\f + \fr 8.21 \ft Yaa 3.4\f*
\v 22 Wa wá gbɛ̃pãle dànɛ́ lↄ. Wa aà laai gwà a gɛ̃na lɛ́ vĩo, wá è a ãiavĩ yã́pii guu, mɛ́ aà ãia ɛ̀a kã̀fĩ tia, kɛ́ a á náai vĩ yã́i.
\v 23 Titu gbɛ̃́ bee sↄ̃, ma zĩkɛndee pↄ́ wi á maa wɛɛlɛ sãnun aà ũ. Wá gbɛ̃́ kĩniↄ sↄ̃, Yesudeↄ zĩnaↄnɛ, aaì Kilisi tↄbↄ.
\v 24 Ayãmɛto à ↄlↄnɛ́ kɛ́ á yeńzi, Yesudeↄ i dↄ̃ kɛ́ wá ĩ́andãa á yã́ musu sĩana vĩ.
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 Má lákɛ̃ɛ́ Lua gbɛ̃́ↄ kↄ̃ kámasa pↄ́ wálɛ kápi yã́ musuo,
\v 2 asa má dↄ̃ a nↄ̀sɛmaa dà, ↄ̃ ma ĩ́anadã̀ Masedoniↄnɛ ma mɛ̀ Gɛlɛkiↄ sↄu mà za muyãa. Á ãiapi ń gbɛ̃́ daside mɛ fɛ̀lɛ.
\v 3 Ɔ̃ ma wá gbɛ̃́piↄ zĩ̀wá àↄ ku sↄu guu lá má òwa, kɛ́ ĩ́ana pↄ́ wá dã̀ yã́pi musu su kɛ pão.
\v 4 Tó Masedoniↄ mↄ̀manↄ, tó aa è á sↄu i mao, wí a wá kũɛ, kɛ́ wa á náaikɛ̀ yã́i. Á è, má á pↄ́ o lↄe?
\v 5 Ayãmɛto má è a maa mà o gbɛ̃́piↄnɛ aa dↄaamɛɛ, aa gba pↄ́ a dↄaa a a lɛgbɛ̃̀ yã́ kɛkɛ káau, a sↄu i ma, iↄ dɛ nↄ̀sɛmɛndo gba ũ, i kɛ gba teaside no.
\s1 Gbadaa ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndoo
\p 
\v 6 À làasookɛ yã́ɛ beewa.
\q1 Tó ń tↄ̃̀ yↄↄ, ni kɛkɛ yↄↄɛ,
\q1 tó ń tↄ̃̀ zↄ̃ↄ, ni kɛkɛ zↄ̃ↄɛ.
\m 
\v 7 Baade kpá lá à zɛ̀ò a sↄ̃ guuwa oosisisai teasisai. Lua ye gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ì gbada ń pↄnaozi.
\v 8 Lua a fↄ̃ to ɛ̀fãai píi liála, gↄↄpii pↄ́pii i mↄ́wá yã́pii guu e à lìála maakɛa píi guu.
\v 9 A kɛ̃a Lua taalau wà mɛ̀:
\q1 Ì pↄ́ fã́ɛ taasideↄnɛ,
\q1 aà maakɛa ìↄ ku gↄↄpiiɛ.\f + \fr 9.9 \ft Soũ 112.9\f*
\m 
\v 10 Lá Lua ì pↄbui kpa pↄtↄ̃nawa mɛ́ ì pↄblea kpa gbɛ̃́piiwa,\f + \fr 9.10 \ft Isa 55.10\f* a pↄbui kpáwá, i kↄ̃́ɛ́, á maakɛa gbɛ i yàasa kṹ.
\v 11 A á kɛ pↄdeↄ ũ yã́pii guu, íↄ gbada sↄũsↄũ gↄↄpii, gbɛ̃́ↄ i Lua sáaukpa gba pↄ́ á dànɛ́ wá sabai yã́i.
\v 12 Asa Lua gbɛ̃́ↄ pↄ́kɛ̃sãma bↄↄlɛ ↄ̃ kámasa zĩpi lɛ́ kɛ adoo, a to Lua sáaukpaa ligua maamaa lↄɛ.
\v 13 Gbɛ̃́ↄ Lua tↄbↄ, asa kámasa pↄ́ á kàpi lɛ́ ↄlↄnɛ́ a misìilɛ Kilisi bao pↄ́ a zɛ̀òɛ, mɛ́ a gbɛ̃kɛkɛ̀nɛ́ ń gbɛ̃́piio ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndoo,
\v 14 aai wabikɛɛ́, aai á nidɛ Lua gbɛ̃kɛ pↄ́ tↄ̃̀wá yã́i.
\v 15 À Lua sáaukpa aà gba pↄ́ gɛ̃̀ oaa yã́i.
\c 10
\s1 Pↄlu gia ń azĩao
\p 
\v 1 Ma Pↄlu, ma awakpàɛ́ ń Kilisi nↄ̀sɛniɛ sùuuo, ma gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ i mɛ má busɛ á guu mɛ́ má pãsĩ á kpɛ.
\v 2 Ma wabikɛ̀wá, tó ma mↄ, ásu to màↄ pãsĩánↄo, asa má fↄ̃ mà a pãsĩ ↄlↄ á gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aaì mɛ dṹnia yã́ mɛ́ lɛ́ dↄaawɛ̃ɛↄnɛ.
\v 3 Wá kú dṹnia guuɛ, ãma wili zĩka lán dṹnia gbɛ̃́ↄwao.
\v 4 Wá gↄ̃kɛbↄↄá dṹnia pↄ́ no, Lua gↄ̃kɛbↄ gbãa pↄ́ wi zɛgikĩi gbooòↄnɛ. Wi ↄ̃nↄ búinaↄ suumpaò
\v 5 ń wala pↄ́ ì gínɛ́ wà Lua dↄ̃o píi. Wi làasoo píi kṹ zĩ̀zↄↄ ũ aa misiilɛ Kilisiɛ.
\v 6 Tó a misìilɛwɛ̃ɛ wásawasa, wá sↄu mà wà swã́gbãadeↄ swã́gaga.
\p 
\v 7 I gbɛ̃́ gwa a bɛawaɛ. Tó gbɛ̃́ dìlɛ Kilisi pↄ́n a ũ, aà ɛa làasookɛ yã́ɛ beewa. Kilisi pↄ́n wá ũ laaàwa sↄ̃.
\v 8 Baa tó ma ĩ́anadã̀ zↄ̃ↄ iko pↄ́ Dii kpàwá yã́ musu, wí a ma kũo, asa á zɛdↄa yã́iɛ, i kɛ á gbooa yã́i no.
\v 9 Má ye ma lákɛ̃aɛ́ àↄ dɛɛ́ vĩadadanzi ũo.
\v 10 Wì mɛ ma láↄ gbia, ì ń gba gbãa, ãma tó wá kú kↄ̃ wɛ́u, ma lɛ́ ìↄ busɛ, ma yã́ lí tↄ̃́máo.
\v 11 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ lɛ́ o màaↄ dↄ̃ kɛ́ lá wá dɛ láↄ guu, màa wáↄ dɛ kua kↄ̃ wɛ́u.
\p 
\v 12 Wá kɛ muaa ge wá wá lɛɛũ ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aalɛ ńzĩa sáaukpaↄo. Aa ńzĩa kpaaĩa ń kↄ̃o ń ńzĩa lɛɛũa ń kↄ̃o ↄ̃nↄ vĩo.
\v 13 Wá gbɛ̃́ beeↄ, wá ĩ́anadã dɛ a lɛ́ao. Wá dã kↄↄ pↄ́ Lua dàwɛ̃ɛ lɛ́uɛ. Baa ápiↄ, kↄↄpi á ká.
\v 14 Lá wa ka á kĩ́i, wálɛ vĩ wá pↄ́ lɛ́ao, asa wa mↄ ń Kilisi baoo e á kĩ́i.
\v 15 Wili ĩ́anadã dɛ a lɛ́a wa gbɛ̃pãleↄ zĩkàuo. Lá á luanaaikɛa lɛ́ kã́fĩ, wá ye zĩ pↄ́ wálɛ kɛ á guu ↄta maamaa e kↄↄ pↄ́ Lua dàwɛ̃ɛ lɛ́uɛ,
\v 16 wí gɛ́ baopi kpái bùsu pↄ́ kú á aɛↄ guu, gbɛ̃pãleↄ tàaabaa ĩ́andãsai.
\v 17 Tó gbɛ̃́ ye ĩ́anadã, aà dã Dii yã́ musu.\f + \fr 10.17 \ft Zel 9.23\f*
\v 18 I kɛ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ì azĩa sáaukpa mɛ́ maao, sema gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ Dii ì aà sáaukpa.
\c 11
\s1 Zĩna ɛgɛnaↄ
\p 
\v 1 À ma fↄ̃ yↄↄ ń ma sↄũkɛyão, ãma álɛ kɛ kↄ̀.
\v 2 Lá Lua lí sí sàao, màa ↄ̃ má kũa á yã́ musu. Á gↄ̃ mɛ̀ndoɛ, ↄ̃n Kilisi ũ. Ma á kpã́sãwà wɛ̃́ndia lɛ́so ũɛ.
\v 3 Lá mlɛ̃ kↄ̃nikɛ̀ Ɛvaɛ à aà sã̀sã,\f + \fr 11.3 \ft Daa 3.1-5\f* vĩa lɛ́ ma kṹ kɛ́ a su á sã́sã sↄ̃, í á naa Kilisiwa gbãsĩsai ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndoo tó.
\v 4 Tó gbɛ̃́ mↄ̀ Yesu yã́ pↄ́ dodo ń wá pↄ́o waasokɛ̀ɛ́, ge nisĩna pↄ́ dodo ń pↄ́ pↄ́ á èo ge baona pↄ́ dodo ń pↄ́ pↄ́ á sìo, i aà gba zɛ́ maamaaɛ.
\v 5 Má è má kɛ̃́sãa zĩna pↄ́ a ń dílɛ dɛńlaↄzi yãe guuo.
\v 6 Baa tó ma lɛ́na nao, má dↄ̃a vĩ. Wá ↄ̀lↄɛ́ ápii wásawasa yã́pii musu.
\p 
\v 7 Kɛ́ ma baona pↄ́ bↄ̀ Lua kĩ́i waasokɛ̀ɛ́ pↄ́siwásai, mɛ́ ma azĩa bùsa á kã́fĩa yã́i, tàae má kɛ̀a?
\v 8 Ma Yesude pãleↄ taiinkɛ̀, ma a asea èmá, kɛ́ mà e màↄ zĩkɛ á guu yã́i.
\v 9 Gↄↄ pↄ́ má kúánↄ, tó pↄ́ lɛ́ kɛ̃́sãa, mili ĩada gbɛ̃ewao. Wá gbɛ̃́ↄ bↄ̀ Masedoni bùsuu, aa mↄ̀mɛɛ ń pↄ́ pↄ́ lɛ́ kɛ̃́sãaↄ.\f + \fr 11.9 \ft Flp 4.15-16\f* Má azĩa kũa, mi kɛ gbɛ̃eɛ aso ũo, mɛ́ máↄ mazĩa kũa màaɛ.
\v 10 Ń Kilisi sĩana pↄ́ kú ma guuo, gbɛ̃e a kpa ma ĩ́andãyãpiɛ Gɛlɛsi bùsuuo.
\v 11 Bↄ́yãi má ò màai? Má yeázi noa? Lua dↄ̃.
\p 
\v 12 Yã́ pↄ́ málɛ kɛ máↄ kɛɛ, kɛ́ mà e zɛzↄ̃ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aalɛ ma lɛ́wɛↄnɛ aa ĩ́anadã láwáwa yã́i.
\v 13 Gbɛ̃́piↄá zĩna ɛgɛnaↄnɛ! Zĩkɛn mↄafilideↄnɛ! Aaì li Kilisi zĩnaↄ ũ.
\v 14 Yãbↄnsaɛ no. Baa Setãupi ì li gupua malaika ũɛ.
\v 15 Lá màaɛ, tó aà zĩkɛnaↄ lì maa zĩkɛnaↄ ũ, yãbↄnsaɛ no. An zia aↄ dɛ ń yãkɛawaɛ.
\s1 Pↄlu taasikɛa a zĩnakɛ guu
\p 
\v 16 Ma ɛa lɛ́ o lↄ, gbɛ̃e su ma gwa sↄũ ũo. Tó màan sↄ̃o, àↄ ma kũa màa, kɛ́ mà e ĩ́anadã yↄↄ.
\v 17 Yã́ pↄ́ málɛ o, Dii mɛ́ ma dauo. Ĩana pↄ́ málɛ dã mazĩa náaikɛa guuɛ bee, málɛ dã mìsaikɛ guuɛ.
\v 18 Lá gbɛ̃́ↄ lɛ́ ĩ́anadã dasi dṹnia yã́ musu, mapi sↄ̃ má dãɛ.
\v 19 Asa á ↄ̃nↄnaↄ i mɛnafↄ̃ ń mìsaideↄ ń pↄnao.
\v 20 Tó wàlɛ á kɛ zↄↄ ũ, tó wàlɛ á só, tó wàlɛ á taiinkɛ, tó wàlɛ gbãablewá, tó wàlɛ á sãnkɛ, i mɛnafↄ̃.
\v 21 Sĩanaɛ, wá busɛ! À kɛ̀mɛɛ wí ũ! Ãma pↄ́ pↄ́ gbɛ̃́ kũa àlɛ a wↄ́ↄ kɛ, má kũa sↄ̃ɛ. Málɛ o mìsaikɛ guuɛ.
\v 22 Ɛbɛluↄ no lò? Má a ũ sↄ̃ɛ. Isailiↄ no lò? Má a ũ sↄ̃ɛ. Ablahaũ buiↄ no lò? Má a ũ sↄ̃ɛ.
\v 23 Kilisi zĩkɛnaↄ no lò? Má a ũ dɛńla. Málɛ yã'o lán ĩ́andewaɛ. Ma zĩkɛ̀ dɛńla, ma daakpɛu dɛńla,\f + \fr 11.23 \ft Zĩn 16.23\f* má a gbɛ̃a lɛ́ dↄ̃o, ma kua ga lɛ́zĩ gɛ̃na lɛ́ vĩo.
\v 24 Yudaↄ ma gbɛ̃ flàala lɛ bla mɛ̀ndosai\f + \fr 11.24 \ft Iko 25.3\f* gɛ̃n sↄo.
\v 25 Wà ma gbɛ̃ ń goo\f + \fr 11.25 \ft Zĩn 16.22\f* gɛ̃n àaↄ̃. Wà ma papa ń gbɛo gɛ̃n do.\f + \fr 11.25 \ft Zĩn 14.19\f* Gó kpàlɛmanↄ gɛ̃n àaↄ̃, ma kɛ ísi guu gↄↄ do fãanɛ ń gwãasĩnao.
\v 26 Ma wɛ̃́lɛ dasi gɛa guu miↄ ku kai guu: Swa kai, kpã́iwɛliwɛↄ kai, Yudaↄ kai, buipãleↄ kai, bɛnanguo kai, sɛ̃̀a kai, ísia kai, Yesude ɛgɛnaↄ kai.
\v 27 Ma zĩ gbãa kɛ̀ ń wãwão, ma itɛ̃kɛ̀ a gɛ̃na lɛ́ vĩo, nↄana ń imio ma dɛdɛ, ma lɛyè a gɛ̃na lɛ́ vĩo, má kú bṹu ĩ́andɛa guu.
\v 28 A kĩniↄ bàasi Yesudeↄ píi kã̀akɛa ìↄ tↄ̃aa lá gu lɛ́ dↄ.
\v 29 Gbɛ̃e bùsa ↄ̃ mi busaoa? Gbɛ̃e fù ↄ̃ i ↄ̃aoa?
\p 
\v 30 Tó a maa mà ĩ́anadãɛ, má dã ma yɛ̃̀ɛɛsaikɛ musuɛ.
\v 31 Lua wá Dii Yesu Kilisi Mae dↄ̃ kɛ́ málɛ ɛɛtoo. Wàↄ aà sáaukpa gↄↄpii!
\v 32 Gↄↄ pↄ́ má kú Damasi, kí Aleta ziia ò wà wɛ̃́lɛpi bĩ́ibↄlɛↄ dã wà ma kṹ,
\v 33 ↄ̃ wà ma bↄ fɛnɛntiu, wà ma pila ń bao gbí guu bĩ́i kpɛ, ↄ̃ ma pilimá.\f + \fr 11.33 \ft Zĩn 9.23-25\f*
\c 12
\s1 Pↄlu wɛ́pungu'ea
\p 
\v 1 À kũ̀ mà ĩ́anadãɛ. Baa tó a ài vĩo, má ɛa su wɛ́pungu'eaↄ ń yã́ pↄ́ Dii ↄ̀lↄmɛɛↄwa.
\v 2 Má gbɛ̃e dↄ̃ naa Kilisiwa, wà aà sɛ̀ gɛ̀ò e luabɛ sĩanau, a wɛ̃̀ gɛ̃o mɛ̀ndosain la. À gɛ̀ ń mɛon nò, mɛsain nò, má dↄ̃o, Lua mɛ́ dↄ̃.
\v 3 Má dↄ̃ kɛ́ wà gbɛ̃́pi sɛ̀ gɛ̀ò e àizãnablekĩi. À gɛ̀ ń mɛon nò, mɛsain nò, Lua mɛ́ dↄ̃.
\v 4 À yã́ pↄ́ a oa kɛo mà, gbɛ̃nazĩna a zɛ́ vĩ à sɛ́lɛ siuo.
\v 5 Má ĩ́anadã gbɛ̃́pi yã́ musuɛ, ãma má ĩ́anadã mazĩa yã́ musuo, sema ma yɛ̃̀ɛɛsaikɛ yã́ bàasio.
\v 6 Tó má ye ĩ́anadã, má ĩ́anadã mìsaide ũo, asa sĩana má o. Ãma má dão, kɛ́ gbɛ̃e su ma dilɛ dɛ lá á è má dɛ ge lá á mà ma lɛ́ulao.
\v 7 Kɛ́ másu mà wala kɛ yãzↄ̃ↄ pↄ́ Lua ↄ̀lↄmɛɛↄ musuo yã́i, à lɛ sↄ̀lↄ ma mɛu Setãu ìwa ũ, àↄ ma gbɛ̃.
\v 8 Ma wabikɛ̀ Diiwa gɛ̃n àaↄ̃ yã́pi musu, aà pↄ́pi gomala,
\v 9 ↄ̃ a òmɛɛ gbɛ̃kɛ pↄ́ i kɛmɛɛ mↄ̀a, yɛ̃̀ɛɛsaikɛ guu ↄ̃ a gbãa sĩana ì bↄu. Ayãmɛto má ĩ́anadã ń pↄnao ma yɛ̃̀ɛɛsaikɛ musu, kɛ́ Kilisi gbãa àↄ kumala.
\v 10 Beewa mi pↄnakɛ ń ma yɛ̃̀ɛɛsaikɛo ń widaaao ń taasikɛao ń ĩadaaao ń wɛ́tɛ̃ao Kilisi yã́i, asa gↄↄ pↄ́ ma busa ↄ̃ miↄ gbãa.
\s1 Pↄlu kã̀akɛa Kↄlɛnideↄnɛ
\p 
\v 11 Ma mìsaikɛ kɛ̀, ámɛ a ma dau. Ámɛ a maa yãa à ma sáaukpa. Baa tó má pↄe ũo, má kɛ̃́sãa zĩna pↄ́ a ń dílɛ dɛńlapiↄzi yãe guuo.
\v 12 Ma a zĩnakɛ seela ↄ̀lↄɛ́ ń mɛnao maamaa yãbↄnsaɛↄ ń dabudabukɛaↄ guu.
\v 13 Bↄ́ ma á kɛ̃́sãò Yesude kĩniↄzii, kɛ́ mi gↄ̃ á gbɛ̃eɛ aso ũo bàasio? À sùuukɛmanↄ ń tàae beeo!
\v 14 Tia kɛ́wa ma mↄa á kĩ́i gɛ̃n àaↄ̃de sↄu mà, mɛ́ má gↄ̃ á gbɛ̃eɛ aso ũo. Ámɛ málɛ á wɛɛlɛ, i kɛ á pↄ́ↄ no. Asa maeↄ mɛ́ aaì àizɛɛ dilɛ ń nɛ́ↄnɛ, i kɛ nɛ́ↄ mɛ́ aali dilɛnɛ́o.
\v 15 Má a pↄ́ↄ ble píi, mí azĩa kpáwá ń pↄnao á wɛ̃ni yã́i. Tó ma yeaázi zↄ̃ↄkũ̀, á yeamazi a lao yã̀?
\v 16 Ɛ̃hɛ̃, mi gↄ̃ɛ́ aso ũo, ãma wà mɛ̀ wɛzɛ̃nan ma ũ, má sìwá ń kↄ̃nioɛ.
\v 17 Ma á blé gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ma ń zĩ́wáↄ kee sabaia?
\v 18 Ma wabikɛ̀ Tituwa aà gɛ́ á kĩ́i, ↄ̃ ma wá gbɛ̃dopi dàɛ̀. Titu á blé yã̀? Wá kã́ doũo lé? Wá tufa doũo lé?
\p 
\v 19 Álɛ e yãa wálɛ bↄkĩi wɛɛlɛ yã̀? Aawo! Wálɛ yã'o ń Lua dↄ̃ao naa Kilisiwa guuɛ. Ma gbɛ̃́ yenzideↄ, ma bee òɛ́ píi á zɛdↄa yã́iɛ.
\v 20 Vĩa lɛ́ ma kṹ, tó ma ka á kĩ́i, kɛ́ másu á le lá má yeiowao, mɛ́ ásu ma e lá á yeiowao. Málɛ vĩakɛ sòleɛ ń zaakↄ̃uo ń pↄkũmao ń dɛnlawɛɛlɛao ń kↄ̃yaaao ń kↄ̃peo ń yↄ̃̀ↄo ń zↄao.
\v 21 Vĩa lɛ́ ma kṹ kɛ́ tó ma ɛa mↄ, ma Lua a to wí ma kṹ á yã́ musu. Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa duunakɛ̀ yãa aa gbãsĩkɛ̀, aa wùlɛ ń gbɛ̃pãle nↄo aa wisaiyã kɛ̀, tó aai mikɛ̃ ń yã́piↄ kɛawao, má ↄ́ↄlↄnɛ́ɛ.
\c 13
\s1 Lɛdama gbɛzã
\p 
\v 1 Ma mↄa á gwai gɛ̃n àaↄ̃den kɛ. Wì yã́si seelade gbɛ̃ↄn pla ge gbɛ̃ↄn àaↄ̃ musuɛ.\f + \fr 13.1 \ft Iko 19.15\f*
\v 2 Má òɛ́ yãa ma kuaánↄ gɛ̃n plaade guu, mɛ́ málɛ oɛ́ lↄ á kpɛ, tó ma ɛa mↄ, má gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa duunakɛ̀ yãaↄ ń gbɛ̃́ kĩniↄ kee tɛ̃boo.
\v 3 Álɛ seela wɛɛlɛ kɛ́ Kilisi mɛ́ lɛ́ yã'o ma guu nolo? Too! I kɛ Kilisi gbãasai no, ìↄ gbãa á guu.
\v 4 Sĩanaɛ, aà paa líwaá gbãasaikɛyãɛ, ãma a kú ń Lua gbãaoɛ. Màa naawà guu wá busɛ sↄ̃, ãma wáↄ kuaànↄ á guu ń Lua gbãaoɛ.
\p 
\v 5 À ázĩa tàasika à gwa, tó á kú Yesu Kilisi náaikɛa guu. À làasookɛ ázĩawa. I dↄ̃ kɛ́ a kú á guuo lé? Tó màa no, a fuaɛ.
\v 6 Má ye àↄ dↄ̃ kɛ́ wápiↄ wi fuao.
\v 7 Wálɛ wabikɛ Luawa ásu vãie kɛo. I kɛ kɛ́ gbɛ̃́ↄ wá maabo yã́i no, kɛ́ à maakɛ yã́iɛ, baa tó wàlɛ wá gwa gbɛ̃́ fuaↄ ũ.
\v 8 Wá fↄ̃ zɛzↄ̃ sĩanaɛo, sema wà zɛpooɛ̀.
\v 9 Tó wá busɛ mɛ́ á gbãa, wá pↄ ìↄ naɛ. Yã́ pↄ́ wi a wabikɛ mɛ́ dɛ kɛ́ á yã́ e àↄ bↄlɛia wásawasa.
\v 10 Ma yã́ beeↄ kɛ̃̀ɛ́, kɛ́ tó ma mↄ, másu wɛbiiwá mà iko pↄ́ Dii kpàa mↄɛ́o. A kpàa á zɛdↄa yã́iɛ, i kɛ á gbooa yã́i no.
\p 
\v 11 Tòo gbɛ̃́ↄ, à gↄ̃̀ zia bàasi. À dɛ̃ɛka á yã́ e àↄ bↄlɛia wásawasa. À ma lɛdama ma. À lɛdoũkɛ àↄ na ń kↄ̃o, Lua yenzide aafiade iↄ kúánↄ.
\v 12 À fↄkpakↄ̃wa ń Lua gbɛ̃́ↄ lɛ́pɛakↄ̃wao. Lua gbɛ̃́ↄ fↄkpàwá ḿpii.
\p 
\v 13 Dii Yesu Kilisi gbɛ̃kɛkɛɛ́, Lua iↄ yeázi, aà Nisĩna iↄ gbɛ̃́kpaaánↄ ápii.
